HEADWORD: Foussa
<hw>Fous"sa</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Natibe
name.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A viverrine animal of Madagascar
(<spn>Cryptoprocta ferox</spn>). It resembles a cat in size and form,
and has retractile claws.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

